    "description": "Mindtree Asia Pacific Associates is actively seeking a talented and motivated Senior Software Engineer to join our dynamic team in Mysuru. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Mindtree Asia Pacific Associates:\nMindtree Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Referral bonus program\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mysuru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Mindtree Asia Pacific Associates!",
